    <div class="bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8 callout">
      <p class="text-lg" style="max-width:none">A GP is a distribution over functions. Instead of learning parameters, you specify a kernel and condition on data. The <strong>posterior is also a GP</strong> — prediction comes with uncertainty for free.</p>
